The '''Kardue family''' was a [[Devaronian/Legends|Devaronian]] family famous because of their staunch support of the [[Devaronian Army]]: The three Kardue'sai'Malloc on the family tree were like their predecessor (though Mika has an unknown posture about that).

The Kardue family was also famous because the criminal [[Kardue'sai'Malloc/Legends|Kardue'sai'Malloc]] the Third, the Butcher of [[Montellian Serat/Legends|Montellian Serat]], was one of its members.

